oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Daily Income Over Feed Cost Value of an Open Day for Holstein Cows
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thorne, James G.
Goodger, William J.
Troutt, H. Fred
Farver, Thomas A.
Scott, Jamon L.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: open day
value
feed costs
detailed production
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The value of an open day for Holstein cows was determined using actual feed costs and detailed production and income records from seven large dry-lot, group-feeding dairies in Tulare County, California, which represent large scale dairy farm technology.
